WEBVTT

21:06.382 --> 21:08.850
So, you're
a Christian
and a Muslim?

21:08.852 --> 21:10.285
And a Hindu,
of course.

21:10.287 --> 21:12.153
And a Jew, I suppose.

21:12.155 --> 21:15.256
Well, I do teach a course
on the Kabbalah
at the university.

21:15.258 --> 21:17.592
And why not?
Faith is a house
with many rooms.
